Okay, this might look like a plea because the Tripreds are un a weak 
position, but it's more for their survival than anything else. There 
are currently only two chars active right now, those being Tyrael and 
Cheetah. I will defend with as much as I can, including base defenses, 
but I will not allow them to die like that. If I can, I'll bring more 
chars in, but I can't guarantee anything. This said, I warn the two 
pred groups that I won't get Tyrael killed and that the base defenses 
are semi-intelligent. If you have any ideas about this situaton, don't 
hesitate to warn me! Thanks!
